-- ECB's Erkki Liikanen Says Financial Regulation `Big Step' Toward Stability
-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 2010-10-05T05:31:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/ecb-s-erkki-liikanen-says-financial-regulation-big-step-toward-stability.html
European Central Bank council member
Erkki Liikanen said the agreed financial market reforms,
including Basel III, are a “big step” toward a more stable
financial system, Liikanen said in the copy of a speech posted
on the Bank of Finland website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
